name: TI-Nspire CX II Operating System File
summary: A TCO2 file is an operating system (OS) file used by Texas Instruments TI-Nspire CX II handheld graphing calculators. It contains an update that can be applied to a calculator's OS. TCO2 files are downloaded and managed using Texas Instruments TI-Nspire Software, which is available for both Windows and macOS.
